~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : charge                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : charge

   This command is used to reload your nerfgun durring nerf conbat.
   You will be warned when your nerf gun is empty.  Every charge gives
   you 5 shots.

   NOTE:  you must be in the designated nerfroom.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : nerf
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
